#

Classic Pickled Jalapeños

25 min
$5
15 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 10

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbVegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

SnacksCondimentsSpicy

Description

Spicy and tangy, these pickled jalapeños add a kick to any dish!

Ingredients

  • jalapeños: 10
  • white vinegar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic cloves: 4
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
  • oregano: 1 teaspoon
